description:
The Good Morning Football Crew share their reactions to the Odell Beckham Jr. comments. The gang also discusses what we learned from week 5. Lastly, Kay Adams, Nate Burleson, Peter Schrager, and Kyle Brandt give you their underappreciated storylines. Be sure to check in every Wednesday to the GMFB podcast! Like, share, subscribe!
